title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 15 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Feb 15 2022
description:
Clay and Buck will broadcast from Mar-a-Lago with President Trump on Tuesday, February 22. New poll shows Biden approval underwater in 46 states. Clay predicts Hillary will be the Democrat nominee in 2024. AOC says crime is on the rise because the Biden child tax credit ran out and people need to steal baby formula. Senator Bill Hagerty of Tennessee joins Clay and Buck to discuss Canada, China, Ukraine, Durham. Montage of media saying there was no spying on Trump.
